    {"type":"text","id":"t_t1_desc","x":80,"y":400,"width":390,"height":40,"text":"* ink: source add PDF/literature\n* Deep research mode for literature discovery\n* 5 sequential Q&A for Gap + Hypothesis\n* 7-dim SCI quality review\n* Content generation (reports, slides)", "fontSize":12,"fontFamily":1,"strokeColor":"#555555","textAlign":"left","verticalAlign":"top","originalText":"* ink: source add PDF/literature\n* Deep research mode for literature discovery\n* 5 sequential Q&A for Gap + Hypothesis\n* 7-dim SCI quality review\n* Content generation (reports, slides)","autoResize":true},

